wiki.summary: "Dalla Dalla" is the debut single by South Korean girl group Itzy, released by JYP Entertainment on February 12, 2019. It was released alongside its music video, and was made available as a digital single titled It'z Different, which features "Want It?" as the B-side. Written by Galactika, the electropop song is a "fusion" track including elements of house and hip hop in which the group emphasizes themes of individuality and self-confidence. Read more on Last.fm.
